---
title: Firecracker Beef Patty Subs with Ponzu Cucumbers & Sweet Potato Wedges
description: You’ve got your classic meatball sub ’n side (marinara, mozz, fries). But how about flipping that script with pork, scallion, ginger, soy meatballs, sharing sub space with crisp ponzu-marinated cukes for bright crunch, and coated with our hall-of-fame firecracker sauce: a creamy, spicy, sweet, and savory number sure to make your taste buds explode! Then, wait for it… a crispy pile of what? Yes! Roasted sweet potatoes (AKA more things to dip in sauce).
